w:0.7'> ٱللَّهَ يَعۡلَمُ مَا فِي ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَمَا فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ </div><div>بِكُلِّ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>شَيۡءٍ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> عَلِيمٌ ٧٩ ٱعۡلَمُوٓاْ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ شَدِيدُ ٱلۡعِقَابِ وَأَنَّ </div><div>ٱللَّهَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>غَفُورٞ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> رَّحِيمٞ ٨٩ مَّا عَلَى ٱلرَّسُولِ إِلَّا ٱلۡبَلَٰغُۗ وَٱللَّهُ يَعۡلَمُ </div><div>مَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>تُبۡدُونَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَمَا تَكۡتُمُونَ ٩٩ قُل لَّا يَسۡتَوِي ٱلۡخَبِيثُ </div><div>وَٱلطَّيِّبُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَوۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَعۡجَبَكَ كَثۡرَةُ ٱلۡخَبِيثِۚ فَٱتَّقُواْ ٱللَّهَ يَٰٓأُوْلِي </div><div>ٱلۡأَلۡبَٰبِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>لَعَلَّكُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تُفۡلِحُونَ ٠٠١ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ لَا تَسۡ‍َٔلُواْ </div><div>عَنۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>أَشۡيَآءَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> إِن تُبۡدَ لَكُمۡ تَسُؤۡكُمۡ وَإِن تَسۡ‍َٔلُواْ عَنۡهَا حِينَ </div><div>يُنَزَّلُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡقُرۡءَانُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> تُبۡدَ لَكُمۡ عَفَا ٱللَّهُ عَنۡهَاۗ وَٱللَّهُ غَفُورٌ حَلِيمٞ </div><div>١٠١</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>قَدۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> سَأَلَهَ